## Project Sentiment Intensity Analysis Aplication

# 1- Scope of the project:

a) at endpoint.py
- Creation of a Chat WEB API integrated with mongodb that allows users to store and display their messages at MongoDB
- This application allows: creating users, creating chats, storing messages and displaying all messages stored in a chat.

b) at appytest.ipynb
- Created a sample chat with a subject, users and messages using script from the Simpsons.
- Created framework code to replace user_id by username on displayed messages and clean the messages.
- Performed Sentiment Intensity Analysis on the sample test to Asses overall positivity, trend of the Sentiment intensity of the Overall conversation, and trend of the intensity of Homer messages.

# 2 Sample test-findings:

![](data:image/png;base64,)

Lineplot on the evolution of the intensity of main sentiment categories alows us to realize that the conversation looses positivity and gains neutrality as time goes by...
